      • addMeasurement

        boolean addMeasurement​(Measurement measurement)
                throws MeasurementException
        Adds a new measurement to the container
        Parameters:
        measurement - measurement to be added to the container
        Returns:
        1. true if the measurement was inserted in the collection storing all measurements
        2. false if the measurement already exists for a given date
        Throws:
        MeasurementException -
        1. if the measurement is null
        2. if the value is lesser than 0
        3. if the date is before the existing last measurement date
        4. if the for a given date the measurement already exists but the values are different
